  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/978b9a0a813106a3d7cc39a894fc8364.webp?t=1662219744\" width=564 height=38 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/09342db0628c5b32b206c4629d06aff8.poster.avif?t=1662219744\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/09342db0628c5b32b206c4629d06aff8.webm?t=1662219744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/09342db0628c5b32b206c4629d06aff8.mp4?t=1662219744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Prepare to Fall.........</i><br><i>A lot.........</i><br><br>Use your tongue as a grappling hook to navigate up an exotic and unforgiving world, while being verbally abused by a flying snake. Be careful, any fall can send you all the way back down...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/4ec8cc761f326dcd168b98f3be845c67.poster.avif?t=1662219744\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/4ec8cc761f326dcd168b98f3be845c67.webm?t=1662219744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/4ec8cc761f326dcd168b98f3be845c67.mp4?t=1662219744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY:</h2><br><strong>Slimefrog is a high stakes fast-paced grappling hook adventure</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Use your tongue as a grappling hook</strong> to climb to the top of an exotic world<br></li><li><strong>Lick platforms</strong> to quickly accelerate yourself towards them.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/cdc78989ba2e7b418ae99b655040063a.poster.avif?t=1662219744\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/cdc78989ba2e7b418ae99b655040063a.webm?t=1662219744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/cdc78989ba2e7b418ae99b655040063a.mp4?t=1662219744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>While mid-air, you only have <strong>4 licks.</strong> These reset every time you land back on the ground or hit a roof.<br></li><li>Get insulted by a flying snake for every mistake</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/b5e4590348937a3e0d63d9a183541ad6.avif?t=1662219744\" width=598 height=138 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE WORLD:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traverse through <strong>9 distinct areas</strong> while being verbally abused by a flying snake.<br></li><li><strong>Listen</strong> to a unique soundtrack with a new track for each level.<br></li><li><strong>Experience </strong>the pain of losing all your progress, and being insulted for it at the same time.<br></li><li><strong>Discover</strong> the dark secret that lies at the top of the world!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/64e86ab396e974fdb0badf6f4af02f08.poster.avif?t=1662219744\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/64e86ab396e974fdb0badf6f4af02f08.webm?t=1662219744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714680/extras/64e86ab396e974fdb0badf6f4af02f08.mp4?t=1662219744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
